data.description:
Kristofer Chun Real Estate proudly presents 501 Kent St.  This lovingly maintained and updated home is located in a quiet neighborhood at the base of Napa’s western hills. This is one of the largest floor plans in the community with a spacious family room, eat-in kitchen with island, separate living room, indoor laundry, 4 bedrooms and 2 and ½ baths. The kitchen boasts newer cabinets, granite counters and stainless steel appliances. The home has new interior paint and the roof is less than 3 years old.

Follow this link to experience an interactive 3D virtual tour: https://my.matterport.com/show/?m=HuufEkfUN6f

Follow this link to enjoy an HD aerial video: https://youtu.be/U5QWxczof4s
